      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p>@Icon[type:graviton] Graviton Revelation</p>\n<p>Your weapons have been exposed to gravity so thoroughly that you can infuse them with gravitational forces with minimal exertion. When you gain an attunement point in graviton mode, you can activate one graviton revelation that grants one of your wielded weapons a weapon special property (such as @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.8IFEg4zF3e0X7HdK]{Attractive Force (Su)}<sup>AR</sup> or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.y7y1SnuR9mbAj3Ux]{Crushing Force (Su)}<sup>AR</sup>) without spending an action. The revelation must have a level of 8 or lower.</p>"
